This folder is intentionally empty. See the project README for why (no
bundled Microsoft-copyrighted sounds, no bundled bitmaps — the UI is drawn
procedurally). Empty directories aren't tracked by git, so this placeholder
file exists just to keep the folder present after cloning; delete it once
you add real files here, and add the folder back to pubspec.yaml's
`flutter: assets:` list if you do.
